{
    "id": "phosphor-flux",
    "name": "Phosphor Flux",
    "category": "Branded",
    "description": "The official Phosphor look. Zones rest on the deep navy brand surface while two depths of luminous gradient ribbons drift through them, ember dust rises with the gradient, bright signal pulses travel a sparse node graph, nested containment strokes breathe inside each zone, and all the borders sample one shared gradient frame with a gleam orbiting each zone. With audio, every ember column rides its own spectrum band, the ribbons warp where the music is loud, bass blooms the graph nodes into small plasma vortices and breathes the shells, and the frame gleams run hotter with the energy.",
